---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Alessandra Ciot | Shiatsu • Moxibustione • Riflessologia">
	<nav class="fixed w-full z-50 bg-[#0a0a0a]/60 backdrop-blur-sm border-b border-white/5 shadow-2xl">
		<div class="max-w-[1600px] mx-auto px-6 py-4 flex justify-between items-center overflow-hidden">
			<span class="font-serif text-l md:text-3xl tracking-tighter font-bold text-white uppercase italic shrink-0">Alessandra Ciot<span class="text-[#00b4d8]">.</span></span>
			<a href="https://wa.me/393489219739" class="group flex items-center gap-3 text-sm font-bold text-[#00b4d8] uppercase tracking-widest shrink-0">
				WhatsApp
				<span class="w-10 h-10 flex items-center justify-center rounded-full border border-[#00b4d8]/30 group-hover:bg-[#00b4d8] group-hover:text-[#0a0a0a] transition-all duration-300 text-xs">
					→
				</span>
			</a>
		</div>
	</nav>

	<main class="overflow-x-hidden">
		<header class="relative min-h-[85vh] md:min-h-screen bg-[#0a0a0a] text-white flex items-center pt-20 md:pt-24 overflow-hidden">
			<div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-[0.03] bg-[linear-gradient(to_right,#888_1px,transparent_1px),linear-gradient(to_bottom,#888_1px,transparent_1px)] bg-[size:64px_64px]"></div>
			
			<div class="max-w-[1600px] mx-auto px-6 grid md:grid-cols-[1fr,auto] gap-8 md:gap-16 items-center relative z-10 py-6 md:py-10">
				<div class="max-w-4xl">
					<div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-[20px] md:text-sm font-medium text-[#00b4d8] mb-4 md:text-base mb-8 uppercase tracking-[0.2em] md:tracking-[0.3em]">
						Percorsi individuali • Tiezzo & Cordenons
					</div>
					<h1 class="text-5xl md:text-[90px] font-serif font-bold leading-[1.0] tracking-tighter mb-10 italic break-words">
						Ritrova <br/><span class="text-[#00b4d8] not-italic">equilibrio, energia</span><br/>e benessere.
					</h1>
					<p class="text-xl text-stone-400 max-w-xl leading-relaxed mb-12 font-light italic">
						Lo Shiatsu non è solo un massaggio, ma una pratica antica che armonizza energia e vitalità. Guidiamo le persone in un percorso personalizzato.
					</p>
					<a href="https://wa.me/393489219739" class="inline-block bg-[#00b4d8] text-[#0a0a0a] px-12 py-5 rounded-full font-extrabold text-lg hover:bg-white transition-all shadow-2xl">
						PRENOTA UN TRATTAMENTO
					</a>
				</div>
				
				<div class="hidden md:block relative">
					<div class="absolute -inset-10 bg-[#00b4d8]/10 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
					<img src="/facendo_trattamento_shia.png" alt="Alessandra Ciot al lavoro" class="relative rounded-3xl w-[500px] h-[650px] object-cover grayscale hover:grayscale-0 transition-all duration-1000 border border-white/10 shadow-2xl" />
				</div>
			</div>
		</header>

		<section class="py-32 bg-[#0f0f0f] border-y border-white/5">
			<div class="max-w-[1600px] mx-auto px-6 grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-20 items-center">
				<div class="order-2 lg:order-1">
					<img src="/leggendo_libro_shia.png" alt="Formazione Alessandra Ciot" class="rounded-3xl w-full max-w-2xl border border-white/5 opacity-80 hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity" />
				</div>
				<div class="grid gap-12 order-1 lg:order-2">
					<div class="group">
						<h3 class="text-white text-2xl font-bold mb-4 uppercase tracking-widest italic font-serif border-l-2 border-[#00b4d8] pl-4">Professionalità certificata</h3>
						<p class="text-stone-500 font-light leading-relaxed italic">Ogni trattamento è eseguito personalmente da Alessandra, operatrice certificata, con anni di esperienza nello Shiatsu.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="group">
						<h3 class="text-white text-2xl font-bold mb-4 uppercase tracking-widest italic font-serif border-l-2 border-[#00b4d8] pl-4">Approccio personalizzato</h3>
						<p class="text-stone-500 font-light leading-relaxed italic">Ogni seduta è adattata alle tue esigenze: ascolto, attenzione e cura del tuo corpo e della tua energia.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="py-24 bg-[#0a0a0a]">
			<div class="max-w-[1600px] mx-auto px-6">
				<div class="text-center mb-16">
					<h2 class="text-[#00b4d8] text-5xl md:text-6xl font-serif italic mb-4">Dove mi trovi</h2>
					<div class="h-[1px] w-24 bg-[#00b4d8]/50 mx-auto"></div>
				</div>

				<div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12">
					<div class="p-6 md:p-12 border border-white/5 bg-[#0f0f0f] rounded-[2rem] hover:border-[#00b4d8]/30 transition-all">
						<h4 class="text-white text-3xl font-serif mb-4 font-bold italic">ASD Bamboo</h4>
						<p class="text-stone-400 font-light italic">Piazza Garibaldi, 26 <br/> 33088 Tiezzo di Azzano Decimo (PN)</p>
					</div>
					
					<div class="p-6 md:p-12 border border-white/5 bg-[#0f0f0f] rounded-[2rem] hover:border-[#00b4d8]/30 transition-all">
						<h4 class="text-white text-3xl font-serif mb-4 font-bold italic">Dream Fitness Wellness</h4>
						<p class="text-stone-400 font-light italic">Via Nogaredo, 78 <br/> 33084 Cordenons (PN)</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section id="servizi" class="py-32 bg-[#0a0a0a]">
			<div class="max-w-[1600px] mx-auto px-6">
				<div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-end mb-20 gap-8">
					<h2 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-serif text-white italic">I Miei <span class="text-[#00b4d8]">Trattamenti</span></h2>
					<div class="md:w-1/3">
						<img src="/facendo_trattamento_2.png" alt="Dettaglio trattamento" class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 transition-all" />
					</div>
				</div>
				
				<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-10 max-w-[1600px] mx-auto text-center md:text-left">
					<div class="group p-6 md:p-12 bg-[#141414] rounded-3xl border border-white/5 hover:border-[#00b4d8]/40 transition-all text-center">
						<h3 class="text-3xl font-serif font-bold text-white mb-3 md:mb-6 uppercase tracking-widest italic group-hover:text-[#00b4d8]">Shiatsu</h3>
						<p class="text-stone-500 font-light italic leading-relaxed text-lg md:text-base">Pressioni manuali profonde per stimolare il flusso energetico e sciogliere le tensioni muscolari.</p>
					</div>
					
					<div class="group p-6 md:p-12 bg-[#141414] rounded-3xl border border-white/5 hover:border-[#00b4d8]/40 transition-all text-center">
						<h3 class="text-3xl font-serif font-bold text-white mb-3 md:mb-6 uppercase tracking-widest italic group-hover:text-[#00b4d8]">Moxibustione</h3>
						<p class="text-stone-500 font-light italic leading-relaxed text-lg md:text-base">Calore mirato su punti specifici per armonizzare l'energia e contrastare disturbi da freddo e umidità.</p>
					</div>
					
					<div class="group p-6 md:p-12 bg-[#141414] rounded-3xl border border-white/5 hover:border-[#00b4d8]/40 transition-all text-center">
						<h3 class="text-3xl font-serif font-bold text-white mb-3 md:mb-6 uppercase tracking-widest italic group-hover:text-[#00b4d8]">Riflessologia</h3>
						<p class="text-stone-500 font-light italic leading-relaxed text-lg md:text-base">Riequilibrio dell'intero organismo attraverso il massaggio zonale dei piedi.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<footer class="py-20 bg-[#0a0a0a] border-t border-white/5 text-stone-600">
			<div class="max-w-[1600px] mx-auto px-6 flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center gap-10">
				<div class="text-center md:text-left">
					<span class="font-serif text-3xl font-bold text-white tracking-tighter uppercase italic">Alessandra Ciot</span>
					<p class="mt-2 text-[#00b4d8] font-bold text-xl tracking-widest">+39 348 921 9739</p>
				</div>
				<div class="text-center md:text-right text-xs uppercase tracking-widest opacity-40 font-mono italic">
					&copy; 2025 Alessandra Ciot • Cordenons • Tiezzo
				</div>
			</div>
		</footer>
	</main>
</Layout>

<style is:global>
	html, body {
		overflow-x: hidden;
		width: 100%;
		position: relative;
	}
</style>